reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute and funtional
reviews.reviewText: We have these in the master bedroom on our night stands and they are pretty functional, trendy, easy to assemble and no complaints.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Wonderful buy - worth it
reviews.reviewText: These are great. Looks pink but truly a beautiful taupe color. Easy to assemble and feel very well made. Thrilled!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Five Star Product in all but one way.
reviews.reviewText: This is a fantastic value....it even includes the dimmable light bulb. Looks classy and beautiful. No downsides to actual product. The lampshade is like nothing I have ever seen in terms of assembly. Fantastic. USB and USB-C ports on the lamp.The only downside and the only thing making this a 4-star review is the packing. Open this product outside of your home, or you will be finding styrofoam in your house forever. The packing materials are not premium and disintegrate upon opening the package. They did their job, which is protecting product in transit, but holy cow that styrofoam was almost as bad as one of those glitter-bombs. Notable enough, to still stress me out. Worth it, absolutely, because of how all around awesome the product is, and great value for two lamps. But....i'm still traumatized by the styrofoam

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 1, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These are very nice. I almost threw away the shades though because they were packed so nice and tight. Easy to assemble. The switch to change the light dimness is sensitive. I end up pushing it a few times lol.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Pretty but not a solid connect.
reviews.reviewText: The lamps are pretty. However the connection from the light portion to the base is not solid. Could be more sturdy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 10, 2023

reviews.reviewText: These lamps were awful quality… poorly designed. They don’t tighten all the way so they are crooked and wobbly and then when you try to unscrew them to fix it, the whole thing comes apart and you cannot put it back together. Most frustrating lamps I’ve ever owned.
